Sentencas: The electrolyte materials BaCe1-xFexO3 (x = 0, 0.1, 0.2, 0.3, 0.4) thick films were synthesized by using the screen printing method and their structural and electrical properties were investigated for solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Effect of Fe-Dopant Addition on the Properties of BaCe1-xFexO3-δ Thick Film as a Solid Oxide Fuel Cells Electrolyte

Sentencas: With increasing addition of Fe2O3, all the thick films showed typical XRD patterns of cubic perovskite structure.
Titulo: Effect of Fe-Dopant Addition on the Properties of BaCe1-xFexO3-δ Thick Film as a Solid Oxide Fuel Cells Electrolyte

Sentencas: The grain size increased up to 0.2 mol% then decreased.
Titulo: Effect of Fe-Dopant Addition on the Properties of BaCe1-xFexO3-δ Thick Film as a Solid Oxide Fuel Cells Electrolyte

Sentencas: The thicknesses of all the films were approximately 25-30 mu m.
Titulo: Effect of Fe-Dopant Addition on the Properties of BaCe1-xFexO3-δ Thick Film as a Solid Oxide Fuel Cells Electrolyte

Sentencas: At x = 0.2, the BaCe1-xFexO3 thick film showed good conductivity and activation energy of 2.98 x 10(-4)
Titulo: Effect of Fe-Dopant Addition on the Properties of BaCe1-xFexO3-δ Thick Film as a Solid Oxide Fuel Cells Electrolyte
